  <section class="docstring">



<p>Joins single process or multiple processes to the group <code class="inline">Group</code>. A process can
join a group many times and must then leave the group the same number of times.</p><p><code class="inline">PidOrPids</code> may contain the same process multiple times.</p>
  </section>
</section>
