          <span class="note">(since OTP 23.0)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/kernel/src/pg.erl#L179" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
