      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Result = {ok, <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:pid/0">pid</a>()} | {error, <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:any/0">any</a>()}</pre>

        </div>


<p>Starts the default <code class="inline">pg</code> scope within supervision tree.</p><p>Kernel may be configured to do it automatically by setting
the Kernel configuration parameter <a href="kernel_app.html#start_pg"><code class="inline">start_pg</code></a>.</p>
  </section>
